sejong.poll.2<-sejong.poll
sejong.poll.2$vote<-factor(sejong.poll.2$vote,levels=c("yes","no"),labels=c("",""))
sejong.poll.2$class<-factor(sejong.poll.2$class,levels=c("high","chief","third.current","third.ex","ordinary"),labels=c(" ","", "3","3",""))
sejong.poll.2$region<-factor(sejong.poll.2$region,levels=c("Seoul","yuhu","gyunggi","pyungan","hwanghae","chungcheong","kangwon","hamgil","gyungsang","jeolla"),labels=c("","","","","","","","","",""))
